'''Müşkapat''' ({{lang-hy| Մուշկապատ}}, also '''Moushkapat''' and '''Mushkapat''') with a latitude of 39.77(39°46′17 N) and a longitude of 46.98(46°58′6 E), is a populated place located in [[Khojavend Rayon]] region of [[Azerbaijan]] that is a part of [[Asia]].

== Location placement ==
[[Mushkapat]] is situated 65 kilometers south west (205°) of the approximate center of [[Azerbaijan]] and 256 kilometers west (255°) of capital [[Baku]].

